<td width="100%" height="100%" align="left" valign="top"><h1>Ventani is Slain....The Sleeper Awakes!</h1>

Tonight, September 14th, 2001, Afterlife killed the 4th warder of Sleeper's Tomb, awakening Kerafyrm, the Sleeper.<br>  As we pulled the final warder, this warning was shouted:
<p>
<img src="/kerafyrm/ventani01.jpg">
<p>
Obviously we didn't heed the warning...Here's a picture of Ventani...not one of his better nights...
<p>
<img src="/kerafyrm/ventani.jpg">
<p>
Shortly after Ventani's death, zones across Norrath came alive with chatter...
<p>
<img src="/kerafyrm/announce.jpg">
<p>
Kerafyrm proceeded to kill everything that moved in Sleeper's.....
<p>
<img src="/kerafyrm/kerafyrm.jpg">
<p>
..... then took his vengeance to the Skyshrine...where the carnage continued. 
<p>
<img src="/kerafyrm/001.jpg">
<p>
<img src="/kerafyrm/01.jpg">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img src="/kerafyrm/02.jpg">
<p>
<img src="/kerafyrm/03.jpg">
<p>
<img src="/kerafyrm/004.jpg">
<p>
<img src="/kerafyrm/04.jpg">
<p>
<img src="/kerafyrm/05.jpg">
<p>
<img src="/kerafyrm/006.jpg">
<p>
<img src="/kerafyrm/06.jpg">
<p>
<img src="/kerafyrm/07.jpg">
<p>
Here is where the sleeper used to lay:
<p>
<img src="/kerafyrm/empty.jpg">
<p>
And here are the people who made it possible...GO AFTERLIFE!!!
<p>
